-- "Black boxes" from Ukraine crash site, under "our control" - rebels
-- By Lina Kushch
-- Sun Jul 20, 2014 07:52AM EDT
-- None



DONETSK, Ukraine, July 20 (Reuters) - A separatist leader said on Sunday items, "presumably" the black boxes from the downed Malaysian airliner, had been found and brought to the eastern Ukrainian city of Donetsk, where they were under "our control".

